# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Accept ownerships
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# AcceptOwnerships reuses all core addresses and ownership variables above.
# Optional timelock accept variables are only required if GOVERNANCE_OWNER,
# TIMELOCK_OWNER, or RISK_GOVERNOR_OWNER is the ProtocolTimelock contract.
